action. DET-PETs give rise to significant changes\nin the binding energies of $^3$H (in the range of approximately 1.5 MeV) and\n$^4$He (in the range of more than 9 MeV) and are able to modify the correlation\npatterns of binding energies of these nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Dec 2011 17:12:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2012 11:01:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-05-30"}
