ices over the two element field) as\nwell as basic properties of the determinant have polynomial-size NC^2-Frege\nproofs, and quasipolynomial-size Frege proofs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2011 10:18:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2013 11:30:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-23"}
